Use the standard library
This is how to get_max_triples of n:
  Remember that count is 0
  Remember that a is 1
  Do this n times:
    When a is less than n, then:
      Remember that b is sum of a and 1
      Do this n times:
        When b is less than n, then:
          Remember that c is sum of b and 1
          Do this n times:
            When c is at most n, then:
              When sum of a and b is more than c, then:
                Increase count
              End when
              Increase c
            But, if not:
              Leave the loop
            End when
          End do
          Increase b
        But, if not:
          Leave the loop
        End when
      End do
      Increase a
    But, if not:
      Leave the loop
    End when
  End do
  The answer is count
Now you know